<ol><li>When the coil spins at a steady rate, the&nbsp;<b>flux linkage changes continuously</b>. At an instant when the normal to the plane of the coil is at angle&nbsp;\(\theta\)&nbsp;to the field lines\[N\phi=BAN\cos\theta\]</li><li>Since&nbsp;\(\theta=\omega t\)\[N\phi=BAN\cos\omega t\]</li><li>The emf is given by\[\varepsilon=-N\dfrac{d\phi}{dt}=BAN\omega\sin\omega t\]</li></ol>